query:
SELECT er.employeeId, e.name, SUM(CAST(er.cash AS DECIMAL(10,2)) + CAST(er.network AS DECIMAL(10,2))) as totalRevenue, dr.date
FROM employeeRevenues er 
LEFT JOIN employees e ON er.employeeId = e.id 
LEFT JOIN dailyRevenues dr ON er.dailyRevenueId = dr.id
WHERE dr.date >= '2025-12-22' AND dr.date <= '2025-12-28'
GROUP BY er.employeeId, e.name, dr.date;
